1
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:35,940
♪Your secret, dangerous flaws♪

2
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:41,620
♪I can stay close
without seeing through♪

3
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:45,610
♪As long as it's about love♪

4
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:46,870
♪No matter how absurd♪

5
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:51,450
♪I choose to get used to it♪

6
00:00:52,810 --> 00:00:56,900
♪Truth or lies, you decide what's true♪

7
00:00:56,970 --> 00:01:00,800
♪I won't overturn it anymore♪

8
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,690
♪I cover my eyes and look♪

9
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:07,860
♪Is love an abyss or a trap♪

10
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:14,710
♪I only see the sparkle♪

11
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:37,980
=Turbulent Love=

12
00:01:38,060 --> 00:01:42,940
=Episode 13=
=Pray Heaven Spares This Couple=

13
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:24,470
Officer Zhou.

14
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:27,030
You're full of surprises!

15
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,120
Why are you so good to me?

16
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:31,800
Do you hate Ji Zhijie too?

17
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,120
I don't do favors for free.

18
00:02:37,710 --> 00:02:38,800
Then what do you want?

19
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:43,240
You just want to mess with Ji Zhijie.

20
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,150
But you're afraid of him.

21
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,240
You can't beat him.

22
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:49,430
I'm handing you his weakness now.

23
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:51,310
Once you kill Ji Zhijie,

24
00:02:52,590 --> 00:02:53,960
give her back to me.

25
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,240
So I can play the hero

26
00:02:56,870 --> 00:02:58,520
and then give me the goods.

27
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:01,470
Officer Zhou.

28
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:05,080
You're negotiating with me?

29
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:08,000
Aren't you afraid
I'll report you to the police station?

30
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:12,470
I have enough dirt on you

31
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,430
to put you in jail for a lifetime!

32
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:19,600
Besides,

33
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:20,500
if you keep these goods,

34
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,120
aren't you afraid Suphan
will come after you?

35
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:26,150
Why not let me sell them for you?

36
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,080
We both profit.

37
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,630
What if I say no?

38
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,840
Coming to see you today means

39
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:38,630
I'm ready to risk it all.

40
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,470
Alright, Officer Zhou.

41
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:44,560
But the price has to be right.

42
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,240
Officer Zhou.

43
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:50,750
I really don't get it.

44
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,800
I get wanting money and power.

45
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:55,590
But now you want her.

46
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,800
And you hand her over to me.

47
00:03:57,330 --> 00:03:58,430
What are you really after?

48
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,430
What Ji Zhijie can or cannot have,

49
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,840
I want it all.

50
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,630
(Ji Zhijie.)

51
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:15,710
(Even if you're Liang Zhaokun's wolf,)

52
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:18,120
(I'm never his lapdog.)

53
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,750
(Everything you want.)

54
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,800
(I'll snatch it all.)

55
00:04:37,460 --> 00:04:40,020
(Pabrik Street No. 27)

56
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,560
Hello?

57
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,600
Hello, Ji Zhijie.

58
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:50,240
Do you like the photos?

59
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,720
You just want to mess with me.

60
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:54,040
I can give you whatever you want.

61
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,000
Let her go.

62
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,160
Listen.

63
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,870
I only give you one hour.

64
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,270
Come alone.

65
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,630
Don't bring anything.

66
00:05:02,430 --> 00:05:04,070
If you dare bring anyone else

67
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,160
or a single gun,

68
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:06,600
or are even a second late,

69
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,720
then I can't guarantee

70
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:10,190
what you'll get.

71
00:05:12,530 --> 00:05:13,720
If anything happens to Hao Yu,

72
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:14,600
you'll get nothing.

73
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,630
And I'll take your life.

74
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:20,560
But you're running out of time.

75
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:22,630
You only have 58 minutes left.

76
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,920
57 minutes and 59 seconds.

77
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,070
58 seconds!

78
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,800
Go back, I'll go alone.

79
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,760
- Zhijie.
- Zhijie.

80
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,640
Ji Zhijie!

81
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,040
A life for a life.

82
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,950
They say Ji Zhijie loves you so much.

83
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:10,950
But why isn't he here yet?

84
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,750
Is he too scared to show up?

85
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:19,920
You must be so disappointed.

86
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:22,150
That's okay.

87
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,800
We can finish what we started

88
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,560
all those years ago.

89
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,400
Look.

90
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,680
I prepared this red bed

91
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,560
especially for you.

92
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:34,430
You're our one and only leading lady.

93
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,800
Has he kissed you here?

94
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,520
What about here?

95
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:55,350
How about

96
00:06:55,830 --> 00:06:57,830
I make a cut right here first?

97
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,440
How does that sound?

98
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,200
Yingquan.

99
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:40,200
You just want revenge for the past.

100
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,510
Come at me instead.

101
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,320
I can give you anything you want.

102
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:49,200
You love playing the hero, don't you?

103
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:51,600
So I had to give you a chance.

104
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,750
She's in the container
right under my feet.

105
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:03,750
But,

106
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,800
where is the key?

107
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:07,350
Ke...

108
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,200
Right here?

109
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,280
Here?

110
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:10,390
I...

111
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:11,470
Here?

112
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:12,750
Here.

113
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,750
Here!

114
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,270
I also heard

115
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:21,120
she's even more afraid of the dark now.

116
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,720
I wonder how

117
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:24,200
she's doing right now.

118
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,390
Listen.

119
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,320
If you want to save her,

120
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:33,000
get on your knees like a dog!

121
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,390
In these broken glass shards,

122
00:09:35,870 --> 00:09:37,080
find the key.

123
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:39,790
Take your time.

124
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:42,320
You don't have much time left.

125
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:46,920
Kneel down!

126
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,910
What a touching scene.

127
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:27,360
It almost makes me cry.

128
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,960
Do you remember

129
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:02,120
how arrogant you were

130
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:03,360
when you slashed my face?

131
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:05,600
I'll never forget it.

132
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:07,150
Did you ever think

133
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:09,240
you'd be kneeling before me

134
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,630
like a dog?

135
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:28,400
♪Don't take amber from my eyes♪

136
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:34,400
♪I'm scared you'll be swallowed by dark♪

137
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:38,160
♪Watching you get tied down♪

138
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:40,280
♪Trapped in the corner♪

139
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:42,800
♪My heart feels torn apart♪

140
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:47,660
♪Even if it's an abyss, I'll fall♪

141
00:11:47,670 --> 00:11:49,550
Time is running out!

142
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:53,680
♪Gray fireworks♪

143
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:57,000
♪Pushing back the bright corners♪

144
00:11:57,400 --> 00:12:00,560
♪Waiting for you to wakeup♪

145
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:04,280
♪Hurts me too much♪

146
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:07,760
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

147
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:11,520
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

148
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:14,280
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

149
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:18,720
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

150
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,390
I'm telling you.

151
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:23,480
You don't have much time left.

152
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:32,320
♪I pray and confess through pain♪

153
00:12:45,890 --> 00:12:50,830
♪Reflecting on the unbearable past♪

154
00:12:52,690 --> 00:12:56,920
♪Like a fire burning my eyes
from within♪

155
00:12:58,310 --> 00:13:00,580
♪I keep touching♪

156
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,780
♪The lines on your palms♪

157
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:05,110
♪Now I know what pain is♪

158
00:13:05,450 --> 00:13:11,600
♪You awakened the me deep in my soul♪

159
00:13:12,590 --> 00:13:15,990
♪Gray fireworks♪

160
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:18,820
♪Pushing back the bright corners♪

161
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,680
Ten.

162
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:22,580
♪Waiting for you to wakeup♪

163
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,440
Nine.

164
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,200
Eight.

165
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:29,920
Seven.

166
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,030
Six.

167
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:36,590
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

168
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,240
Five.

169
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,200
Four.

170
00:13:44,430 --> 00:13:48,170
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

171
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,240
Three.

172
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:54,630
♪I pray and confess through pain♪

173
00:13:57,190 --> 00:14:00,110
♪I learned to let go of myself♪

174
00:14:00,870 --> 00:14:03,630
♪I burn away every bitter result♪

175
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:05,230
♪Just to light♪

176
00:14:05,390 --> 00:14:09,390
♪Eternal fireworks for you♪

177
00:14:09,950 --> 00:14:13,070
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

178
00:14:13,070 --> 00:14:16,910
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

179
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:19,590
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

180
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:24,030
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

181
00:14:24,230 --> 00:14:27,390
♪Don't leave me to survive alone♪

182
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:31,390
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

183
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:37,510
♪I pray and confess through pain♪

184
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:46,390
♪Only your love can♪

185
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:50,450
♪Take away the pain♪

186
00:14:56,270 --> 00:14:57,150
Hao Yu, are you okay?

187
00:14:57,150 --> 00:14:57,990
I'm fine.

188
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:04,600
Stay still if you don't want to die.

189
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,200
I know you won't let me go.

190
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,120
But as agreed, let Hao Yu go.

191
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:15,390
Do you think

192
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,720
I'm that trustworthy?

193
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:21,080
Then I deserve to die knowing the truth.

194
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:23,750
I need to confirm something
before I die.

195
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:24,910
Alright.

196
00:15:25,030 --> 00:15:26,510
Go ahead, I'll grant your last wish.

197
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,630
Speak.

198
00:15:29,670 --> 00:15:30,670
You saved Weihao

199
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,790
and lured Zhong Jiali
to ally with you, right?

200
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:35,630
Of course.

201
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:03,270
If Liang Zhaokun wasn't such a tyrant

202
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:04,840
and you weren't so blinded by love,

203
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,360
causing so much resentment,

204
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:07,910
I wouldn't have had a chance.

205
00:16:08,670 --> 00:16:09,670
You killed Suchart.

206
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:11,440
After learning Zhong Jiali
failed to get the goods,

207
00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:12,910
you incited Weihao to kill me

208
00:16:12,910 --> 00:16:13,790
and take those goods.

209
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:15,480
Right?

210
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,510
Who does Suchart think he is?

211
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,030
Using his brother's status,

212
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:21,200
he dared to boss me around.

213
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:23,390
He's just like you.

214
00:16:23,670 --> 00:16:24,630
You both deserve to die!

215
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,030
What did you do to him?

216
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:29,120
I destroyed his body

217
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:30,840
and framed you for it.

218
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:33,840
So you could seize power

219
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:36,030
and get revenge on me.

220
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:38,030
After taking the goods,

221
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,910
so you think you can
boss Suphan around, right?

222
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,230
Bingo!

223
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:43,320
I'll not only boss him around.

224
00:16:43,390 --> 00:16:44,840
I'll boss you around too!

225
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,670
I'll take everything

226
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:48,270
you have.

227
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,960
And wipe out your Cangfeng!

228
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:52,720
You knew today was a death trap.

229
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:53,750
Yet you still came.

230
00:16:54,990 --> 00:16:55,860
Then I'll have to

231
00:16:55,870 --> 00:16:58,200
fulfill your tragic love story.

232
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:01,120
I'll kill you all.

233
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,720
Then return to Seronport

234
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,160
and rule Southeast Asia.

235
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:05,790
Rule Southeast Asia!

236
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,590
Go to hell!

237
00:17:09,030 --> 00:17:10,440
You heartless Yingquan!

238
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:12,000
Dreaming of ruling Southeast Asia?

239
00:17:12,060 --> 00:17:13,070
Pay for my brother's life!

240
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:26,590
Ji Zhijie.

241
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:28,160
A life for a life.

242
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:30,310
You scum killed my brother

243
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:32,200
and stole the goods meant for me.

244
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,880
Yet you still dare to look for me?

245
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:35,390
Bring it on!

246
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:36,960
I'll send you to hell right now!

247
00:17:55,170 --> 00:17:57,150
I looked for you
because I thought you're reasonable.

248
00:17:57,300 --> 00:17:58,880
I don't have time to explain.

249
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:00,790
If you want to know who killed Suchart,

250
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:01,960
come with me to Yingquan's place.

251
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,880
Once you know the truth,

252
00:18:04,210 --> 00:18:05,310
you must cooperate with me.

253
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:09,030
Why should I trust you?

254
00:18:12,830 --> 00:18:14,550
Yingquan's territory is also yours.

255
00:18:14,750 --> 00:18:15,590
I'm all alone now.

256
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:16,790
What trouble could I possibly cause?

257
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:23,830
Pay for my brother's life!

258
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:27,440
I swore not to kill.

259
00:18:27,450 --> 00:18:28,720
You take him. I'll find the goods.

260
00:18:34,210 --> 00:18:35,180
I'll go look for the goods.

261
00:18:35,190 --> 00:18:36,030
You wait here.

262
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,750
I... I'll go with you.

263
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:02,440
It's not a total loss.

264
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:16,670
Zhijie.

265
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:18,160
- Feilong, take him alive.
- Yes.

266
00:19:18,350 --> 00:19:19,380
Feihu, move the goods now.

267
00:19:19,390 --> 00:19:20,310
Before something goes wrong.

268
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:21,390
Got it.

269
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:23,800
It's okay now.

270
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,920
- It's okay. You're safe.
- It's okay.

271
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:27,840
You're safe now.

272
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:28,800
It's over.

273
00:20:47,250 --> 00:20:49,070
(Police Station)
Have him fill out this form.

274
00:20:49,310 --> 00:20:50,680
- Right.
- Keep a close eye.

275
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:51,590
Let's go.

276
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,030
Get this straight.

277
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,550
We are the victims here.

278
00:20:59,510 --> 00:21:01,420
You failed to protect us.

279
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:04,130
You let my wife get kidnapped.

280
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,000
And I got injured.

281
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:07,000
Instead of catching the culprit,

282
00:21:07,210 --> 00:21:08,200
why did you bring me here?

283
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,960
Please watch your language.

284
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:17,830
Legally, you are not married.

285
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:33,440
Whether we are married or not

286
00:21:33,440 --> 00:21:34,550
is none of your business.

287
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:41,030
Is Officer Zhou
holding a personal grudge?

288
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,510
We received a tip.

289
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:51,880
Suspecting you of illegal trading.

290
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,590
Leading to a public disturbance.

291
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:57,830
Please cooperate with our investigation.

292
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:03,480
Zhou Ziheng, I'm warning you.

293
00:22:05,310 --> 00:22:07,400
If you do anything
out of line to Hao Yu,

294
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,830
I don't know what I'll do.

295
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:18,440
Mr. Ji, please calm down.

296
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,000
We're all law enforcers.

297
00:22:20,550 --> 00:22:21,480
And Officer Zhou

298
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:23,000
is the best officer we have.

299
00:22:23,730 --> 00:22:24,960
This is a legal interrogation.

300
00:22:25,270 --> 00:22:26,510
If nothing is found,

301
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:28,030
we'll release you right away.

302
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:30,800
You'd better.

303
00:22:32,310 --> 00:22:33,510
My lawyer is on the way.

304
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:38,910
Okay.

305
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,480
Watch him.

306
00:23:21,790 --> 00:23:23,440
I've turned off the audio and cameras.

307
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:25,640
You can speak freely now.

308
00:23:46,270 --> 00:23:47,110
Hao Yu.

309
00:23:58,880 --> 00:23:59,960
Did you hear what I said?

310
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,510
What do you want me to say?

311
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:10,480
Where are the goods?

312
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:15,550
How did you find me?

313
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:21,800
I told you

314
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:24,000
we have more than one mole

315
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:25,720
and informant.

316
00:24:26,270 --> 00:24:28,400
Didn't your informant and mole know

317
00:24:29,550 --> 00:24:30,880
that I was drugged, kidnapped

318
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:33,160
and almost died there?

319
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:39,430
I'm sorry.

320
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:40,960
You went through so much.

321
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,040
Do you still remember

322
00:24:49,510 --> 00:24:51,240
what your kidnapper looked like?

323
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:52,760
Any memory of him?

324
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,590
You can tell my colleagues.

325
00:24:56,030 --> 00:24:57,400
We can help you find him.

326
00:24:59,000 --> 00:24:59,960
I'm not afraid of dying.

327
00:25:01,880 --> 00:25:02,880
For my parents,

328
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,520
my brother,

329
00:25:04,790 --> 00:25:05,920
and Mr. Guan

330
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:07,550
to rest in peace,

331
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:11,030
I chose this path of revenge myself.

332
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:16,070
I promised godfather

333
00:25:17,790 --> 00:25:20,400
to do things legally and justly.

334
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:26,270
Of course I know that.

335
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:28,510
That's exactly why

336
00:25:29,310 --> 00:25:31,270
we must finish this mission quickly.

337
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,160
I'm really worried about you.

338
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,350
Have you ever truly worried about me?

339
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:46,000
If it weren't for Ji Zhijie

340
00:25:46,270 --> 00:25:47,200
and Suphan today,

341
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,440
I would have died there!

342
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:53,790
Ji Zhijie, Ji Zhijie.

343
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:54,720
Ji Zhijie!

344
00:25:57,590 --> 00:25:59,590
You keep saying he did so much for you.

345
00:26:00,590 --> 00:26:01,480
What about me?

346
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:09,000
To keep you from being exposed,

347
00:26:10,590 --> 00:26:11,720
I played along with you

348
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,680
to frame Weihao.

349
00:26:14,300 --> 00:26:15,270
Then I destroyed the data

350
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:16,640
and framed Zhong Jiali.

351
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:19,560
I risked my life

352
00:26:20,900 --> 00:26:22,720
to apply for a special mission
from the police station

353
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:23,640
to catch Ji Zhijie.

354
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:26,590
All to take down Cangfeng.

355
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:30,270
I even got injured

356
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,480
and demoted.

357
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:34,720
Everything I did

358
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:38,000
was to hide your identity
as an informant.

359
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:39,680
So Cangfeng wouldn't find out.

360
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:42,310
Can't you see that?

361
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:53,390
Or

362
00:26:55,410 --> 00:26:56,880
have you fallen in love with Ji Zhijie?

363
00:27:00,110 --> 00:27:01,310
You want to betray Mr. Guan?

364
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:03,590
I'm not the one betraying Mr. Guan.

365
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,720
I was drugged and kidnapped today.

366
00:27:20,510 --> 00:27:22,270
Ji Zhijie and Suphan saved me.

367
00:27:25,270 --> 00:27:26,960
I saw someone stealing the goods.

368
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:29,630
That guy

369
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,640
even shot at me.

370
00:27:33,310 --> 00:27:34,150
And then,

371
00:27:35,110 --> 00:27:36,000
by coincidence,

372
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:37,790
we ran into you.

373
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:39,070
And you brought us here.

374
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,070
That's everything that happened today.

375
00:27:48,030 --> 00:27:48,870
Alright.

376
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:52,350
Yingquan is dead.

377
00:27:54,070 --> 00:27:56,070
I heard Suphan is in Seronport too.

378
00:28:02,750 --> 00:28:03,960
Ji Zhijie will probably

379
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:05,160
finish this deal soon.

380
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:08,510
Your mission now

381
00:28:08,510 --> 00:28:10,550
is to find the goods
as soon as possible.

382
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:13,030
And tell me right away.

383
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:15,720
Why do you care so much about the goods?

384
00:28:17,550 --> 00:28:18,550
Shouldn't we

385
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:20,030
investigate their deal

386
00:28:20,030 --> 00:28:21,350
and take them all down?

387
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:24,800
Right.

388
00:28:26,070 --> 00:28:27,270
Of course that's what I think.

389
00:28:37,350 --> 00:28:38,190
Hao Yu,

390
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,760
how are you?

391
00:28:41,950 --> 00:28:42,800
Are you okay?

392
00:28:42,800 --> 00:28:43,710
Did he hurt you?

393
00:28:48,590 --> 00:28:49,430
I'm fine.

394
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:52,400
But look at you,

395
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:56,960
you're a mess
and still worrying about me.

396
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,480
My husband is badly injured.

397
00:29:04,780 --> 00:29:06,070
If Officer Zhou has nothing else,

398
00:29:06,160 --> 00:29:07,070
we'll be leaving now.

399
00:29:07,510 --> 00:29:08,400
Feilong, let's go.

400
00:29:08,500 --> 00:29:09,480
We're going to the hospital.

401
00:29:10,410 --> 00:29:11,830
Better have the doctor
come to the house.

402
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:12,720
Hurry.

403
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:14,560
Let's go.

404
00:29:15,510 --> 00:29:16,880
I'm fine. They're just scratches.

405
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:17,950
Don't talk.

406
00:29:18,830 --> 00:29:19,790
Okay, okay.

407
00:29:20,550 --> 00:29:21,390
Alright.

408
00:29:21,750 --> 00:29:22,680
It's not the first time.

409
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:31,110
Hao Yu, I'm really fine.

410
00:29:31,110 --> 00:29:32,350
These are just scratches.

411
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:33,800
I'm perfectly fine.

412
00:29:39,270 --> 00:29:40,160
What if

413
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:44,640
Suphan's men hadn't shown up today?

414
00:29:51,030 --> 00:29:52,960
Shanmao just wanted to
show me who's boss.

415
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:54,800
As long as I'm alive,

416
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:56,310
he can torture me all he wants.

417
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:57,750
Your safety's all that counts.

418
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:06,510
Alright, alright.

419
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,350
Don't cry.

420
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:09,760
Don't cry.

421
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,520
We're both safe now.

422
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:12,640
It's all my fault.

423
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,680
I should've had someone protect you.

424
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:18,880
Don't cry.

425
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:20,480
Don't cry.

426
00:30:23,270 --> 00:30:24,110
It's okay.

427
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:29,830
Do you still remember

428
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:32,110
how they kidnapped you?

429
00:30:39,510 --> 00:30:40,350
I...

430
00:30:40,510 --> 00:30:42,240
I was just

431
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:46,000
going to buy something,

432
00:30:47,590 --> 00:30:50,110
and then I took a shortcut.

433
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:55,240
I'm sorry.

434
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:56,720
It's okay.

435
00:30:57,680 --> 00:30:58,520
It's fine.

436
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:04,840
Ji Zhijie,

437
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:08,560
why?

438
00:31:09,830 --> 00:31:11,350
You're clearly a bad guy,

439
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:14,830
but you're always so good to me.

440
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:18,510
Always showing up when I need you most.

441
00:31:40,070 --> 00:31:40,910
Time for your medicine.

442
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:49,030
It's too bitter.

443
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,590
Now I need a little

444
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,200
sweet reward.

445
00:31:59,280 --> 00:32:00,310
It works better than medicine.

446
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:39,200
♪Don't take amber from my eyes♪

447
00:32:41,080 --> 00:32:45,200
♪I'm scared you'll be swallowed by dark♪

448
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:48,960
♪Watching you get tied down♪

449
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:51,080
♪Trapped in the corner♪

450
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:53,600
♪My heart feels torn apart♪

451
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:59,200
♪Even if it's an abyss, I'll fall♪

452
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:04,480
♪Gray fireworks♪

453
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:07,800
♪Pushing back the bright corners♪

454
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:11,360
♪Waiting for you to wakeup♪

455
00:33:11,360 --> 00:33:15,080
♪Hurts me too much♪

456
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:18,560
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

457
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:22,320
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

458
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:25,080
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

459
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:29,520
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

460
00:33:29,720 --> 00:33:32,920
♪Don't leave me to survive alone♪

461
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:36,800
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

462
00:33:37,280 --> 00:33:43,120
♪I pray and confess through pain♪

463
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:48,600
♪I learned to let go of myself♪

464
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:52,120
♪I burn away every bitter result♪

465
00:33:52,120 --> 00:33:53,720
♪Just to light♪

466
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:57,880
♪Eternal fireworks for you♪

467
00:33:58,440 --> 00:34:01,560
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

468
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:05,400
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

469
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:08,080
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

470
00:34:08,240 --> 00:34:12,520
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

471
00:34:12,720 --> 00:34:15,880
♪Don't leave me to survive alone♪

472
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:19,880
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

473
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:26,000
♪I pray and confess through pain♪
